mruthyunjaya ( kannada : ಮೃತ ಯುಂಜಯ ) is a 1990 indian kannada action drama film directed by chi .   dattaraj while the story , screenplay , dialogues and lyrics are written by chi . udaya shankar .   the film features shivarajkumar , malashri and shashikumar in the lead roles .   produced by raghavendra rajkumar under vajreshwari combines , the film screened for over hundred days in the cinema halls .